{"tid":307997,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"綠茶同抹茶分別？","createTime":"2017-07-03T19:31:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-04T15:05:58.000Z","uid":117161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e9b6632cdc6f9a98b7885341fc79eeb46b0d0e5a","tid":307997,"uid":117161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T19:31:49.000Z","msg":"一直都以爲分別只在於一個來自中國一個來自日本<br />\n但大致上都係差唔多野 只係叫法唔同<br />\n但個朋友同我講係兩樣好唔同既野 仲叫我係出邊買雪糕果陣唔好搞亂<br />\n究竟個分別係咪真係咁大<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2315743fa9943cbac2baa5accc07995685054be","tid":307997,"uid":36551,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T19:35:28.000Z","msg":"參考下<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"http://www.tokichi.jp/chinese_traditional/tea/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.tokichi.jp%2Fchinese_traditional%2Ftea%2Findex.html&d=omeP7BZpcxedT4OJKrQBIAKEmdudW1rq3V1Y15kzxIU%3D&h=8fab6f79\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.tokichi.jp/chinese_traditional/tea/index.html</a>"},{"pid":"828f1e46015c6759afecd93a8ec5afa1d69a01c0","tid":307997,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T20:03:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/41.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04782779f75a17773bf00666ce4efb283cc4cdb7","tid":307997,"uid":70293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T20:31:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>參考下<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"http://www.tokichi.jp/chinese_traditional/tea/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.tokichi.jp%2Fchinese_traditional%2Ftea%2Findex.html&d=omeP7BZpcxedT4OJKrQBIAKEmdudW1rq3V1Y15kzxIU%3D&h=8fab6f79\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.tokichi.jp/chinese_traditional/tea/index.html</a></blockquote><br />\n以為煎茶=綠茶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37d4e14934c853511a7ff598c79230e3a91c1e5a","tid":307997,"uid":76242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T20:40:02.000Z","msg":"抹茶=茶粉<br />\n綠茶=完整茶葉<br />\n抹茶好似冇炒過"},{"pid":"33167e9ec81934e761497ff0f6831be00c8e1879","tid":307997,"uid":52056,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T01:36:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>抹茶=茶粉<br />\n綠茶=完整茶葉<br />\n抹茶好似冇炒過</blockquote><br />\n日本綠茶殺青係用蒸而唔係炒<br />\n綠茶係一個大類, 茶葉殺青之後唔發酵, 所以碧螺春, 龍井都係綠茶<br />\n日本綠茶就有抹茶, 玉露, 煎茶, 莖茶, 焙茶(焙茶有用火烘過所以係啡色, 但茶葉本身冇發酵)<br />\n<br />\n日本綠茶同平時茶葉沖嘅茶差唔多, 不過靚茶有種海苔鮮味(飲開中國綠茶嘅話會飲唔慣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n抹茶就茶葉磨粉開水, 口感濃厚, 茶味同苦味都重過綠茶<br />\n所以買咗唔同茶做嘅甜品真係差好遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3aa0bec5f7e6015fc60755ce85b62d6f52aa7f1d","tid":307997,"uid":2020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T01:42:09.000Z","msg":"簡單講<br />\n<br />\n抹茶係茶葉磨成粉 <br />\n沖出黎茶湯大多為綠色<br />\n<br />\n綠茶係茶葉沖泡出黎 <br />\n茶湯偏淺色 透明又有 青色又有 淡黃又有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90e965894765aec306353499a300e5e6dbe53f09","tid":307997,"uid":52793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T01:48:05.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"3c5799fc69824093ea0310a1efcc1949cbef85d0","tid":307997,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T03:55:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>抹茶=茶粉<br />\n綠茶=完整茶葉<br />\n抹茶好似冇炒過</blockquote><br />\n日本綠茶殺青係用蒸而唔係炒<br />\n綠茶係一個大類, 茶葉殺青之後唔發酵, 所以碧螺春, 龍井都係綠茶<br />\n日本綠茶就有抹茶, 玉露, 煎茶, 莖茶, 焙茶(焙茶有用火烘過所以係啡色, 但茶葉本身冇發酵)<br />\n<br />\n日本綠茶同平時茶葉沖嘅茶差唔多, 不過靚茶有種海苔鮮味(飲開中國綠茶嘅話會飲唔慣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n抹茶就茶葉磨粉開水, 口感濃厚, 茶味同苦味都重過綠茶<br />\n所以買咗唔同茶做嘅甜品真係差好遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n長智識 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1a0ee5bafaeae4c7f43bf7c94eee8ffcd178ebd","tid":307997,"uid":29929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T03:59:21.000Z","msg":"青蘋果綠茶係咩綠茶"},{"pid":"57ae032c25de5194569ee4a4584bfd7dbe698f54","tid":307997,"uid":117161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T04:23:41.000Z","msg":"咁姐係食甜品或者雪糕之類都唔洗太執著係綠茶定抹茶，反正都係差唔多，味道唔太大分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86acaefd08bff00818f95da237be6275ddfdab42","tid":307997,"uid":52056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T15:05:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁姐係食甜品或者雪糕之類都唔洗太執著係綠茶定抹茶，反正都係差唔多，味道唔太大分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n大家覆咗咁多個post點解你可以出到呢個結論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">雖然平價綠茶/抹茶甜品味道又真係唔會差太遠</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}